{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.640", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Januar dieses Jahres hat die Bundesregierung die Fragen der Fraktion Die Linke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.720", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in den vorliegenden Antrag eingeflossen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.600", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bereits ausf\u00fchrlich beantwortet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.720", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im M\u00e4rz dieses Jahres hat sich der Bundestag erneut intensiv mit dem Thema BAf\u00f6G auseinandergesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.160", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Regierungsparteien haben sich im Koalitionsvertrag bereits auf einen weiteren Ausbau im Bereich des BAf\u00f6Gs verst\u00e4ndigt und werden zus\u00e4tzliche Mittel bereitstellen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.960", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dies, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.520", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nachdem die Bundesregierung in drei Stufen das BAf\u00f6G seit 2015 beispiellos reformiert hat und seitdem auch dauerhaft den Finanzierungsanteil der L\u00e4nder \u00fcbernommen hat."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.000", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum Antrag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.080", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zun\u00e4chst einmal ist es nicht beklagenswert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.480", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern positiv, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.520", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass weniger Studenten BAf\u00f6G beantragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass weniger die Antragskriterien erf\u00fcllen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.000", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "W\u00e4ren die Zahlen anders, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.600", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich steigend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.080", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann w\u00fcrden Sie von der Linkspartei uns hier in eine Armutsdebatte verstricken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.000", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sollten sich also freuen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.720", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es immer mehr Menschen in unserem Land wirtschaftlich so gut geht und weniger Studenten auf staatliche Unterst\u00fctzung angewiesen sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.560", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie behaupten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Studenten mit dem BAf\u00f6G nicht auskommen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.600", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weshalb sie nebenher arbeiten m\u00fcssten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.160", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dies f\u00fchre dann zu \u00fcberlangen Studienzeiten und erh\u00f6he die Zahl der Studienabbr\u00fcche. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.600", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie beklagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass im derzeitigen BAf\u00f6G-Satz nur 250\u00a0Euro f\u00fcr die Unterkunft angesetzt sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.760", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was nicht ausk\u00f6mmlich sei, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.240", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und fordern eine drastische Erh\u00f6hung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.000", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die durchschnittliche Bruttowarmmiete in den deutschen Studentenwohnheimen"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.760", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "betr\u00e4gt laut Deutschem Studentenwerk 241\u00a0Euro."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.280", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ich als Student also bereit bin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.000", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mich mit einem Zimmer im Studentenwohnheim zu begn\u00fcgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie das Zigtausende von Studenten \u00fcber Generationen getan und gut \u00fcberstanden haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.280", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann sollte ich mit dem Geld hinkommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.960", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es schadet niemandem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.160", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn er in jungen Jahren noch Luft nach oben hat und bescheidener startet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.680", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Studenten-WG oder das Zimmer im Wohnheim machen doch den Charme des Studentenlebens aus."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.840", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daher ist es auch falsch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.000", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu fordern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.480", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das BAf\u00f6G m\u00fcsse in der H\u00f6he an die Leistungen f\u00fcr den Lebensunterhalt nach dem SGB\u00a0II angepasst werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.560", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Lebenssituationen von Studenten und Beziehern von Grundleistungen sind nicht vergleichbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.000", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Finanzielle Einschr\u00e4nkungen f\u00fcr die wenigen Jahre des Studiums sind zumutbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.640", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil Studierende nach erfolgreicher Beendigung ihres Studiums eine gute Einkommensperspektive haben; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.400", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Kollege Dr.\u00a0Brandenburg ist darauf ja schon eingegangen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.600", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ebenso ist schon immer ein gro\u00dfer Teil der Studenten in den Semesterferien einem Ferienjob nachgegangen oder hat dauerhaft nebenher ein paar Stunden gearbeitet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.360", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Etliche haben es getan, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.600", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um mehr Geld zur Verf\u00fcgung zu haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.200", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "viele aber auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.160", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Kontakte in Betriebe zu bekommen und um ihr theoretisches Studium um erste praktische Einblicke in das Berufsleben zu erg\u00e4nzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.040", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer nebenher ein paar Stunden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.160", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meist handelt es sich um einen 450-Euro-Job\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.320", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "arbeitet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kann immer noch im vorgesehenen Rhythmus seine Scheine machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.120", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zumindest haben das Generationen von Studenten unter Beweis gestellt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.520", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die hohe Zahl der Studienabbrecher h\u00e4ngt sicherlich nicht damit zusammen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.800", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Studenten mit wenig Geld auskommen m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.760", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Ursache liegt oftmals darin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.400", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir zwar mehr Abiturienten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.720", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nicht mehr Bildung haben"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.800", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dass das Abitur in vielen Bundesl\u00e4ndern nicht mehr die Studierf\u00e4higkeit garantiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.760", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein gro\u00dfes Thema, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "289.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "293.880", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das aber nicht in die Kompetenz des Bundestages f\u00e4llt!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "293.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.240", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie stellen hier gro\u00dfe Forderungen nach einem bedingungslosen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "300.880", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "staatlich finanzierten Einkommen von Studenten auf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "300.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.040", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Antwort, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "304.920", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie diese Mehrkosten finanziert werden sollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "304.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.240", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bleiben Sie schuldig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.440", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und Sie problematisieren Bereiche, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "314.120", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in den letzten Jahren bereits engagiert angegangen wurden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "314.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "316.040", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit der dritten Stufe der Reform, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "316.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "319.920", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zum Wintersemester\u00a02016/2017 in Kraft trat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "319.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "324.360", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wurden die Bedarfss\u00e4tze um immerhin 7\u00a0Prozent angehoben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "324.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.720", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch der Wohnzuschlag wurde \u00fcberproportional angepasst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "327.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "331.720", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ebenso wurden die Einkommensfreibetr\u00e4ge angehoben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "331.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "335.920", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Vereinbarkeit von Familie und Ausbildung wurde verbessert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "335.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "345.720", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im aktuellen Koalitionsvertrag wurden Mittel in H\u00f6he von 1\u00a0Milliarde Euro f\u00fcr den weiteren Ausbau der BAf\u00f6G-S\u00e4tze verankert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "345.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "356.280", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Ministerin wird weiterhin regelm\u00e4\u00dfig die H\u00f6he des BAf\u00f6G-Satzes \u00fcberpr\u00fcfen und gegebenenfalls Anpassungen und Weiterentwicklungen vornehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "356.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "361.520", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kollegin Staffler hat es vorhin schon ausgef\u00fchrt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "361.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "368.120", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Durch immer weiteres Aufw\u00e4rmen Ihrer Vorstellungen werden diese nicht besser. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "368.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "370.920", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Thema ist l\u00e4ngst in der Mache. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "370.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "375.400", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb kann ich abschlie\u00dfend nur sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "375.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "378.840", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann bekanntlich jeden Drops nur einmal lutschen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "378.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "381.400", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und der Drops ist bereits gelutscht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "381.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "382.480", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich danke Ihnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "382.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "393.360", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gestatten Sie mir einen kurzen Hinweis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "393.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "397.480", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in diesem Fall in die Reihen der Fraktion Die Linke: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "397.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "401.880", 
